c851fbw">Thuỷ điệu ca - 水調歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%AD-Dung/author-2_qWM98BFZN9xS_LN9XQ4w">Trương Tử Dung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-NNj51-ebZyApj8ndjN6_VQ">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Lu%C3%A2n/V%C3%A3n-th%E1%BB%A9-Ng%E1%BA%A1c-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-YTZ8DDMGoP0V6pgDXGf7Dw">Vãn thứ Ngạc Châu - 晚次鄂州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Lu%C3%A2n/author-VVZ_VDVd2wfprGEnIm6L6g">Lư Luân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-qu%C3%A1ch/poem-LEv6IBeaFP8jJ3mpwVI9Kw">Xuất quách - 出郭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
